Results:

The healthcare prediction system successfully:

Predicted disease diagnosis from medical indicators
Identified critical healthcare features
Compared classification model performance
Improved interpretability using feature importance analysis

Random Forest and XGBoost produced strong classification performance for multi-class disease prediction.

Ethical AI and Patient Privacy

This project highlights important healthcare AI principles:

Patient Privacy
No personally identifiable information (PII)
Data anonymization
Secure model storage
Privacy-aware preprocessing
Explainable AI
Feature importance analysis
Transparent model evaluation
Interpretable healthcare predictions
Human Oversight

The system is designed to assist healthcare professionals and not replace clinical decision-making.
